_sText:
This map is a remake of the old he_glass cs 1.6 map.
suitable for up to 30 players, you start off with a knife and smoke grenade with nades lying on the floor.
the objective is to break the glass on the enemy spawn to kill the enemy when they fall to their death.
please rate and comment..
have fun :D
p.s there is a scout in the middle if you can get to it
